---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <section class='flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-16'>
    <h1 class='text-3xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4'>¿Razones para amarte?</h1>
    <p class='text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 text-center max-w-2xl px-4'>Cada día descubro nuevas razones para amarte más, eres mi inspiración y mi felicidad</p>
    <span class='text-gray-700 mb-4'>(En este pdf podras encontrar las razones)</span>
    <a href='/Razones.pdf' download>
      <span class='bg-pink-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-700 transition-colors cursor-pointer font-bold shadow-lg'>DESCARGA PDF</span>
    </a>
  </section>
  <section class='flex justify-center items-center w-full max-w-screen h-[600px] relative overflow-x-hidden'>
    <div class='flex flex-col items-center px-2 relative z-10'>
      <div class='z-10'>
        <h1 class='text-4xl font-semibold uppercase text-white text-center'>Te Amo</h1>
        <h1 class='text-xl flex items-center gap-2 text-white'>
          <span>✨</span>
          <span class='text-center'>mas que un simple infinito</span>
          <span>✨</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class='heart absolute -z-10'></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .heart {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background-color: #ff4b4b;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    position: absolute;
    top: -50px;
  }

  .heart::before,
  .heart::after {
    content: '';
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background-color: #ff4b4b;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
  }

  .heart::before {
    left: -150px;
  }

  .heart::after {
    top: -150px;
  }
</style>
